    <lb n="1"/>τῷ δεσπότῃ μου καὶ ἀδελφῷ καὶ κυρίῳ τῆς ψυχῆς μου Κοπρέᾳ 

    <lb n="2"/>Ἑρμαπόλλων. 

    <lb n="3"/><choice><corr>προηγουμένως</corr><sic>προηκουμενως</sic></choice> <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.293">πολλά σε</lem><rdg><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">πό</unclear>λλαν</rdg></app> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">π</supplied>ροσαγορεύω νυκτὸς <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">κ</supplied>αὶ <choice><corr>ἡμέρας</corr><sic>ημεραις</sic></choice> τῷ <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>ψίστῳ θεῷ καὶ παρὰ 

    <lb n="4"/>πᾶσι ἀνθρώποις <choice><corr>προσκυνῆσαί</corr><sic>προσγυνησαι</sic></choice> <choice><corr>σου</corr><sic>σο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear></sic></choice> τὸ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ε</supplied>ὔμορφον καὶ <hi rend="diaeresis">ἱ</hi>λαρὸν πρόσωπον <choice><corr>πρωτοτύπως</corr><sic>προτ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">οτ</supplied>υπως</sic></choice>. 

    <lb n="5"/>μετὰ τὸν θεὸν ἄ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λλ</unclear>ον ἀδελφὸν οὐκ ἔχω οὔτε φίλον γνήσιον οὔτε εὐπροαίρετον ἄνθρωπον εἰ μὴ 

    <lb n="6"/>σὺ μόνος. ὁ κύριος θεὸς γὰρ <app type="BL"><lem resp="7.90"><choice><corr>μαρτυρεῖ</corr><sic>μαρτυρι</sic></choice> ὅτι οὔτε</lem><rdg>μαρτύριο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear> <choice><corr>ὅτι</corr><sic>ουτε</sic></choice></rdg></app> τὰς νύκτας <choice><corr>κοιμῶμαι</corr><sic>κυμωμαι</sic></choice> <choice><corr>κλαίων</corr><sic>κλεων</sic></choice> καὶ εὐχόμενος καὶ παρα-

    <lb n="7"/>καλῶν τὸν θεὸν <hi rend="diaeresis">ἵ</hi>να <choice><corr>σε</corr><sic>σαι</sic></choice> ἀπολάβω εὐθυμοῦντα καὶ εὐπυγ<g type="apostrophe"/>μοῦντα καὶ ὁλοκληροῦντα. ἐδή-

    <lb n="8"/>λωσέν με γὰρ ἡ μήτηρ μου περὶ τῶν <choice><corr>εὐποιιῶν</corr><sic>ευποιειων</sic></choice> σου, κύριέ μου ἄδελφε, <gap extent="3" reason="lost" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ω</unclear>ται τῶν <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear><gap extent="3" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="9"/>ἐμαρτυρήθῃ μ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>ι δέ, κύρ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ιε μου ἄδε</supplied>λφε, <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>πὸ τῆ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ς </supplied><app type="BL"><lem resp="1.293"><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">κυρία</supplied>ς</lem><rdg><gap extent="5" reason="lost" unit="character"/></rdg></app> μου Λούρα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ς ὡς ἡ</supplied> μήτηρ μ<supplied cert="low" reason="lost">ου οὐκ</supplied> ἐ-

    <lb n="10"/>δυνήθη ἀπαντῆσαι πρ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὸς </supplied><app type="BL"><lem resp="1.293"><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἐ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μ</unclear>ὲ δ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ιὰ τὸ</supplied></lem><rdg><gap extent="2" reason="lost" unit="character"/>αδ<gap extent="5" reason="lost" unit="character"/></rdg></app> μὴ ἔχει<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν </supplied><gap extent="8" reason="lost" unit="character"/>α καὶ <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">νμ</unclear><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 

